item_spikes.text_en: Tear - More spells but still some mana problems
item_spikes.text_fr: Tear - Plus de spells mais encore des problèmes de mana

item_spikes.text_en: Catalyst - More dmg, tankier, no more mana problems
item_spikes.text_fr: Catalyst - Plus de dmg, plus tanky, plus de problèmes de mana

item_spikes.text_en: Dirk - Damage doubles, hurts a lot more
item_spikes.text_fr: Dirk - Dégâts doublés, fait beaucoup plus mal

item_spikes.text_en: Youmuu - Very fast, 1-shot wave or Q+E = 400 dmg alone
item_spikes.text_fr: Youmuu - Très rapide, 1-shot wave ou Q+E = 400 dmg seul

item_spikes.text_en: 1st base - Mega tanky, harder to kill
item_spikes.text_fr: 1st base - Mega tanky, plus dur à kill

item_spikes.text_en: Full Boots - Way easier trades with E MS + boots MS
item_spikes.text_fr: Full Boots - Trades beaucoup plus faciles avec E MS + boots MS

item_spikes.text_en: Lost Chapter - Can trade without going OOM
item_spikes.text_fr: Lost Chapter - Peut trade sans aller OOM

item_spikes.text_en: Malignance - Ult on much shorter CD, more spammable
item_spikes.text_fr: Malignance - Ult sur CD beaucoup plus court, plus spammable

item_spikes.text_en: Tear - More mana, more angles to trade
item_spikes.text_fr: Tear - Plus de mana, plus d'angles pour trade

item_spikes.text_en: Catalyst - Very tanky, can chase you down
item_spikes.text_fr: Catalyst - Très tanky + pas mal de mana, peut te run down

item_spikes.text_en: RoA - Very tanky + sustain from passive
item_spikes.text_fr: RoA - Très tanky + sustain du passif

item_spikes.text_en: Rylai - Perma slow makes life miserable
item_spikes.text_fr: Rylai - Slow perma, ça va te rendre malheureux

item_spikes.text_en: Gonna rush Hollow Radiance if you are AP : he's unkillable + he os waves
item_spikes.text_fr: Va rush Rayonnement du vide si t'es un AP : il est intuable + il one tap les waves

item_spikes.text_en: Gonna rush Rocketbelt if you are AD : he deals a lot of dmg
item_spikes.text_fr: Va rush Rocketbelt si t'es un AD : peut te tuer si t'as 60% hp sur un combo

item_spikes.text_en: HE'S THANOS
item_spikes.text_fr: C'EST THANOS

item_spikes.text_en: Dark Seal — first back, good HP sustain and damage
item_spikes.text_fr: Sceau Noir - Premier back, bon pull d'hp + damage

item_spikes.text_en: Rush Sorcerer’s Shoes as a first item to run you down quickly
item_spikes.text_fr: Rush 1st item Chaussures du sorcier généralement pour te run dessus rapidement

item_spikes.text_en: Diana becomes very strong in skirmishes with Protobelt + ult
item_spikes.text_fr: Diana devient très forte dans les skirmish avec protobelt + ult
